There are three layers of the
structure from facade to slab (from
exterior to interior):
1. Exterior wall panels with an
insulating layer; 2. Window frame;
3. slab support and other support
structure.
The exterior wall takes the load of the
whole building.
Dowel laminated timber
Advantage:
Greater structural eﬃ ciency for one-
way spans than CLT;
cheaper than CLT;
With no nails or metal fasteners,
DowelLam panels can be easily
processed using CNC machinery and
allow on site modiﬁ cations
Disadvantage:
Over time, hardwood fasteners or
dowels lose their stiﬀ ness causing
dimensional instability.
